project: Norega is a an IDLE-RPG hybrid that can be played actively or by idling... Norega is a game where your main task is to send your champion on adventures by clicking the -GATES- and after returning from your adventure you can use your collected treasure to upgrade your character stats by clicking the other buildings. (LIFE = YOUR HEALTH) (ATTACK = YOUR ATTACk)  (WIS = EXP GAIN) and (MAGICAL DAMAGE) (GR == GOLD GAIN) (GAIN == LOOT GAIN)
